headline: Snap-on Incorporated Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: KENOSHA, Wis., April 24, 2025--The Snap-on board declared a quarterly dividend of $2.14 per share payable June 10, 2025, to shareholders of record on May 20, 2025.
